  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Max Ranks:</strong> 5 </p><p>• A <strong>Chilled</strong> Creature has its body and nerves overwhelmed by cold. Once per turn when they willingly move more any number of feet, they take 1d6 cold damage for each rank they have.</p><p> • A <strong>Chilled</strong> creature's speed is reduced by 5 feet for every rank it has.</p><p> • A creature takes a -1 Penalty to all Dexterity based Checks &amp; Saving throws, for each rank they have. </p><p>• A creature resistant or Immune to Cold Damage also has resistance or immunity to this condition. This condition lasts for the duration of the effect that inflicted it or 1 minute has passed, whichever comes first.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
